           cause != null ? cause.getMessage() : "null");
  
   // ── Step 1: is this failure worth sending to AI? ──────────────────────
   if (!isHealableFailure(cause)) {
       System.out.println("[SelfHealingListener]    → Not healable (assertion/logic failure). Skipping AI.");
       HealingRegistry.markSkipped(scenarioId);
